urlText: Central Station: Access changes due to Sydney Metro construction works
content:
From 10pm Friday 12 to 4am Monday 15 February 2021, the escalators and lifts between the Grand Concourse and Northern Concourse at Central Station will be closed for Sydney Metro construction works.

Alternative stairs, escalators and lift are available outside the Opal gates. Please follow the signs and staff directions.

If you need assistance, see station staff.

Platforms 20, 21
